Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.03,0:00:08.12,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(75,75)}It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.37,0:00:11.59,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.76,0:00:15.03,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,As power passes through our clasped hands
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.18,0:00:18.68,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's grab hold of our wishes{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.32,0:00:32.51,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Working together, let's ride the giant waves{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.30,0:00:31.85,OP11 Credits,,50,0,230,,Translation\N FUNimation
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.55,0:00:37.02,OP11 Credits,,450,0,280,,Soundtracking\NHalee
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.55,0:00:37.02,OP11 Credits,,0,450,350,,Infoboxes/Title Card\N BernieCrane
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.14,0:00:41.03,OP11 Credits,,0,100,420,,Editing\NFeeso
